JOHANNESBURG - Reports have emerged that former eNCA anchor and MTN group executive for corporate affairs, Chris Maroleng has been appointed as the new SABC COO. If the appointment pans out, Maroleng will fill the post following Hlaudi Motsoeneng's ousting last year. WATCH: 'Hlaudi is a brand,' says Hlaudi The SABC has reportedly said the process of appointing a new COO is still underway and has not made an official announcement about a COO appointment. Morloleng's LinkedIn profile still lists him as working as Executive: Group Corporate Affairs at MTN Group.  eNCA